linux-4.7.2-galliumos (4.7.2-galliumos4) xenon; urgency=medium

  * New patch: allow-gpio-lookup-fallback-by-boot-param.diff
    - Adds kernel boot param gpiolib.acpi_lookup_can_try_crs.
      + If set (=1), ACPI GPIO lookups can fallback to _CRS
      + Bay Trail byt-max98090 audio driver requires _CRS lookups
  * Disable patch: revert-acpi-gpio-lookups-patch-10cf499.diff
    - Superseded by previous

 -- reynhout <reynhout@galliumos.org>  Wed, 21 Sep 2016 16:23:58 +0000

